# Sprites are NOT shipped or hosted. At runtime the app fetches them from
# Digi-API into the user's browser (with consent) and caches them on the user's
# device (src/ui/spriteEngine.ts). The committed manifest (src/assets/cutouts/)
# is name-only fallback data, not art.
#  - sprites-src/ : dev cache of raw source PNGs for the optional QA bake.
#  - tools/out/   : QA bake output (cutouts + contact sheet), dev only.
#  - public/cutouts/ : never committed and never built into the deploy.
tools/sprites-src/
tools/out/
public/cutouts/

